{"tid":2361084,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【tvN韓劇 女神降臨】韓劇現海量植入式內地廣告惹熱議 激嬲韓國網民：以為係睇大陸劇","createTime":"2021-01-10T10:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:54:15.000Z","uid":49004,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8596c9eee2a0160a588f31032cac2a4d8c42eac1","tid":2361084,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"車銀優、文佳煐、黃仁燁主演的tvN韓劇《女神降臨》改編自同名人氣漫畫，集合外貌出眾的演員吸引不少劇迷追看，而香港觀眾一樣可以在黃Viu煲劇平台收看。但最近播出的集數就引起韓國網民熱議，皆因出現不少內地植入式廣告，大量的廣告鏡頭令劇迷看得一秒出戲，更有網民表示「以為係睇大陸劇。」<br />\n<br />\n《女神降臨》目前為止已播出8集，但就已經多次出現植入式內地廣告，令不少觀眾都大感出戲。在第4集中，講述女主角任朱靜（文佳煐飾）為與男生約會尋找靚衫，在苦惱之陣卻意外發現姐姐任熙靜（林世美飾）的房間中，擺放著中國購物網站的快遞箱，成功找到一條連身裙前往約會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108114833_0_a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108114833_0_a2.jpg&h=3a779fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108114834_2_a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108114834_2_a4.jpg&h=d90729a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108114835_3_a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108114835_3_a5.jpg&h=09b52f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今星期播出的第7集，在男女主角李修豪（車銀優飾）和任朱靜即將帶來粉紅泡泡曖昧場面之陣，兩人身後的巴士站就出現巨型內地購物網站的宣傳海報，再次令觀眾感到奇怪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115318_0_b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115318_0_b3.jpg&h=b96bef86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115319_1_b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115319_1_b4.jpg&h=afb6e0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115320_2_b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115320_2_b5.jpg&h=010aa976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115320_3_b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115320_3_b6.jpg&h=4e0b7155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115321_4_b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115321_4_b1.jpg&h=b063b44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115322_5_b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115322_5_b2.jpg&h=42a800a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後續劇情之中，女主角任朱靜與同學姜秀貞（朴柔娜飾）一起到便利商店吃東西時，竟然不是出現韓劇常見的杯麵或飯糰，而是內地品牌推出的速食火鍋，而後方的易拉架及海報同樣是該速食火鍋的廣告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115630_0_c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115630_0_c6.jpg&h=6e1a5cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115631_1_c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115631_1_c1.jpg&h=78c753b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115632_2_c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115632_2_c2.jpg&h=d2605e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115632_3_c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115632_3_c3.jpg&h=df4481c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115633_4_c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115633_4_c4.jpg&h=212c44db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/202101/20210108115634_5_c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F202101%2F20210108115634_5_c5.jpg&h=517b9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這些植入式廣告都引起不少韓國網民討論，有不少人感到不滿直言太誇張「明明係韓國背景，但出現漢字海報和食品」、「以為係睇大陸劇」、「太多海外產品廣告令人反感」等等，不過都有網民表示「只要專心看主演們的臉就好」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213677/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F213677%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7dB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c868137e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213677/</a>"},{"pid":"ae12b56345346e6d7037cc36a592ee6912877bcd","tid":2361084,"uid":3852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"好在韓國網民都反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4f888a351f87d264018506bb05a0564534d111","tid":2361084,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"真係over左嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e305d0ac3614cbcdebe3e1ed4a61523073a283","tid":2361084,"uid":355997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"柒到 一浸支那味出哂嚟"},{"pid":"74d3328715eac5f8842c29446b2d826e3752d57b","tid":2361084,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"京東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd9a7b4115bfdbc263dbe8f09154afe417aa215","tid":2361084,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"重柒過D家庭劇無啦啦送禮D直入廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}